n using this with CMAKE?\r\n\r\nIt uninstalls the GLFW library, headers and package files from where the `install` target placed them (or will place them).\r\n\r\n> How do we disable it?\r\n\r\nIt's disabled along with the `install` target. Use the `GLFW_INSTALL` CMake option to disable them.\r\n\r\n> It is not mentioned in the documentation, nor any of the code within the \"install\" target CMakelists itself.\r\n\r\nTrue, and it really should be included. There isn't really a section on installation at all and the rest of the compilation guide isn't all that great either.\r\n\r\n> If it must exist can it be automatically added inside the `GLFW3` folder instead of outside it?\r\n\r\nAbsolutely! Fixed with aef4edadd0b580fd55a93299ac171caade586fe8.","author_association":"MEMBER","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/comments/344611902/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"elmindreda","id":133714,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEzMzcxNA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/133714?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda","html_url":"https://github.com/elmindreda","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url"